comment_data.body: It looks like `TypeIdNode` (which was the other node to default to error_type) is a bit of a mess of fully analysing its operand (which is possibly partly my fault... not 100% sure!). Thus it's pretty fragile to changes like this. Blocking `type_dependencies` seems to fix it, but it isn't a hugely satisfactory solution really.

I'll mark this as draft for the moment and change it properly later...
